{"tid":659333,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[ I/A ] Brown Dust (26) - 盲既先抽盲盾","createTime":"2018-05-09T17:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T17:21:50.000Z","uid":24752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db93aede84947e1ceae7276bfee22f65f84c41a9","tid":659333,"uid":24752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">韓國 NEOWIZ 3月6日宣佈戰略指令RPG《Brown Dust》（iOS/Android）預定於3月7日正式配信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg&h=4930ba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg&h=e2c3f92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg&h=8ea46a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg&h=48b52cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg&h=09636aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg&h=40f0c136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg&h=74ffb367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg&h=00fb64b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg&h=658c68d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg&h=ae7b04f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg&h=226e900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲核心內容是陣營配置，先在戰前佈置我方十體傭兵角色，再在戰鬥階段時接雙方角色的攻勢移動順來互相攻擊。作品之內有多達300名角色，而且全都均可提升至最高階級別。<br />\n<br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1299021478&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4bf0adad\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478</a><br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=495a1987\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global</a><br />\nQooApp：<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F6042&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=936de352\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042</a></div>"},{"pid":"73ab964b68485418edf8f2935790d3ba9991cb50","tid":659333,"uid":24752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【照顧絲打/基巴區】</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg&h=d16019f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg&h=9bb96aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg&h=85fe362e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195812_821682b225905978953e0f97e65b0ab9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195812_821682b225905978953e0f97e65b0ab9.jpg&h=2be19d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195814_abf34b3c931bee1138125c896371a5d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195814_abf34b3c931bee1138125c896371a5d9.jpg&h=772e1c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/123528_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F123528_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=75182308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【攻略】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">日版速刷首抽方法 (遊戲內建)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32104&amp;snA=4&amp;tnum=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D32104%26snA%3D4%26tnum%3D3&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=237c14e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32104&amp;snA=4&amp;tnum=3</a><br />\n右上角設定<br />\nPLUG下方那排日文 點下去<br />\n打上Reset 就重來了</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【日本評價網】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wiki.denfaminicogamer.jp/browndust/%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0?comment=3#comment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.denfaminicogamer.jp%2Fbrowndust%2F%25E3%2583%25AA%25E3%2582%25BB%25E3%2583%259E%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25AD%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25B0%3Fcomment%3D3%23comment&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8c4cca7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.denfaminicogamer.jp/browndust/%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0?comment=3#comment</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【大陸仔評價】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/125048_6967ff941a69d01c51db4931a80684c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F125048_6967ff941a69d01c51db4931a80684c4.jpg&h=6206e282&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.ngacn.cc/attachments/mon_201803/07/bwQ5-6cy1ZfT3cSoa-hs.jpg.medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ngacn.cc%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201803%2F07%2FbwQ5-6cy1ZfT3cSoa-hs.jpg.medium.jpg&h=5733e4be&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【升星方法】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://c.kekeke.cc/t/FmVevFK97u.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.kekeke.cc%2Ft%2FFmVevFK97u.jpeg&h=1498bddf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n張圖死左, 大致上就係刷一般券抽狗糧(銀色星既角色), 升LV, 跟住昇級由1星升2星, 2星升3星, 漫漫長路升到5星再比5星角食<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【韓服圖鑑】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!ZBAUWIKY!XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21ZBAUWIKY%21XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0ea5e925\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!ZBAUWIKY!XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8</a></div>"},{"pid":"8e95fd6f8b2e1913ab2dedc8a0bff4005bbeef4d","tid":659333,"uid":18196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"3樓做歐皇"},{"pid":"014e44dca262ffc35a5af19d23dad66d3a589d35","tid":659333,"uid":24752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A:<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚洗唔洗刷首抽<br />\nA:最好就刷 因為抽五星機率只係1% 十次十連都唔中係經常既事<br />\n<br />\nQ:刷到歌基+是但一隻開唔開波好<br />\nA:開 再問就ban<br />\n<br />\nQ:課咩野包係最抵屌<br />\nA:新手500%<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚好似好複雜 唔知點樣玩<br />\nA:呢隻驚好似捉棋咁 放錯人錯順序都會影響哂成場結果 自己慢慢摸索啦<br />\n<br />\nQ:好多體力唔知點洗好<br />\nA:新手一開始就衝主線 唔夠打就刷符紋/肥料升主力<br />\n<br />\nQ:無錢又無肥 幾時先有得刷肥關<br />\nA:星期五至日或日本假期特定時間 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZCbmg74XISk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZCbmg74XISk&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9af178a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZCbmg74XISk</a><br />\n打錢關最快放法<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽咩pool好<br />\nA:盲既先抽盲盾<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽到好多三星做唔做升星肥好<br />\nA:唔做 好多三星都有用 廢既就將佢+9 兩隻+9合一隻原四<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽到重覆五星食唔食好<br />\nA:隻野勁就食 廢就做升星肥<br />\n<br />\nQ:sup狀態會放邊 唔識用<br />\nA:下一個順序<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚肝唔肝<br />\nA:唔肝、因為可以掛機打素材，但係唔會失樂趣 因為掛機成日會唔夠打 而且pvp 公會戰 地下城 搶礦 打符文高層 全部都係要用腦去諗同試 <br />\n<br />\nQ:無課玩唔玩到<br />\nA:玩到 育成Game課左只會資源黎得較快 <br />\n<br />\nQ:六魔星點有<br />\nA:無得首抽 用魔幣換<br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣買體係最抵<br />\nA:神秘島係有粉既情況 係交易所用石刷商店買體 抵過直接用石買<br />\n<br />\nQ:敏捷有咩用<br />\nA:被攻擊時有機率觸發減35%傷 debuff持續時間減半<br />\n<br />\nQ:盾既減傷點計<br />\nA:盾既減傷係乘上去,最高70%減傷,盾同減傷實測係同一樣野,敏捷可以另外疊加,盾+敏捷可達80.5%減傷<br />\n<br />\nQ:可唔可以一次過升星 逐隻逐隻禁好煩<br />\nA:可以 去升星畫面左下個傭兵選擇 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/124319_df4328360824ac5145095d454cd2a143.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F124319_df4328360824ac5145095d454cd2a143.png&h=514166a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 邊隻先解到歌雞招魅惑？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091402_3a0de14d008f7c694837eca11f394deb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091402_3a0de14d008f7c694837eca11f394deb.png&h=ac04bad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA: 隻驚分免疫同淨化，免疫只可以防止中，已經中咗既話無用<br />\n淨化只可以解，未中既話無用<br />\n免疫：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091518_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091518_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png&h=9e2ad084&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091527_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091527_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png&h=2eb9f16a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淨化：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091538_abf557f17822f530a5457e4ab1cadc95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091538_abf557f17822f530a5457e4ab1cadc95.png&h=020f904c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091916_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091916_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=768cb619&s={SIZE}\" />呢兩個咩黎?<br />\nA:上面係暴擊率，下面係暴擊時既額外傷害[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nQ:SET左掛機之後去訓覺, 唔通又要較埋鬧鐘起身閂機?<br />\nA:<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tcleg0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTcleg0r.jpg&h=e83d4f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:綠盾要點先有?<br />\nA:去傭兵合成果度合, 用4隻4星合出黎, 其中阿叔果隻4星係用4隻3星合, 當中最難有果隻臭雞(アセラ)要用P點抽<br />\n<br />\nQ:任務個30日FEST我有日唔小心做唔完, 係咪收得皮?<br />\nA:30日既意思係你30日內每日做晒就最快30日拎到, 做慢左咪遲D拎到, 做完會繼續有第2個30日重新開始<br />\n<br />\nQ:符文6星R勁d定係5星UR勁d?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://teasoku.com/%E3%80%90%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3%E3%83%80%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%80%91%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%81%AE%E5%8A%B9%E7%8E%87%E3%81%AE%E3%81%84%E3%81%84%E9%9B%86%E3%82%81%E6%96%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fteasoku.com%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E3%2583%2596%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2582%25A6%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2583%2580%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2583%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2583%25AB%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2581%25AE%25E5%258A%25B9%25E7%258E%2587%25E3%2581%25AE%25E3%2581%2584%25E3%2581%2584%25E9%259B%2586%25E3%2582%2581%25E6%2596%25B9&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=efcf283d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://teasoku.com/%E3%80%90%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3%E3%83%80%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%80%91%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%81%AE%E5%8A%B9%E7%8E%87%E3%81%AE%E3%81%84%E3%81%84%E9%9B%86%E3%82%81%E6%96%B9</a>"},{"pid":"cbc07b331d4622547b0db254548bf719f106a596","tid":659333,"uid":13275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">post 27呀，砍!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8bb0746d3e58cf4b686c2374be57be1aa0bc503b","tid":659333,"uid":18196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"26+1=26 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}